TESTIMONY TIME

0:02:59.760,0:03:04.480
My name is Joana Agboga, I am from Edo State but I reside in Abuja.

0:03:04.480,0:03:06.020
I'm a student.

0:03:06.020,0:03:12.600
I came to thank God for delivering me from the evil spirit that caused me to bedwet,

0:03:12.600,0:03:19.880
steal, lie, be angry and very stubborn.

0:03:19.880,0:03:26.940
I started bedwetting from when I was small.

0:03:26.940,0:03:31.780
When I would bedwet, I'd wake up and feel that the bed was wet and stand up.

0:03:31.780,0:03:35.140
Most times, I would cry and tell my mum.

0:03:35.140,0:03:37.420
It was every night.

0:03:37.420,0:03:41.100
It had been happening on a day to day basis.

0:03:41.100,0:03:45.860
As for the stealing, I would go to a supermarket with a huge sum of money

0:03:45.860,0:03:50.860
but pick up something worth 50 or 20 naira and leave.

0:03:50.860,0:03:53.320
I would not use it.

0:03:53.320,0:03:58.020
I would just take it and throw it away; sometimes, I would keep it.

0:03:58.020,0:04:02.020
I had the spirit of anger.

0:04:02.020,0:04:06.640
I used to get angry at any little thing.

0:04:06.640,0:04:10.220
When I got angry, I would bang the door on my mum.

0:04:10.220,0:04:14.260
If someone hid money in the house, something would tell me where the money was.

0:04:14.260,0:04:18.860
I would go there and get the money no matter where they hid it.

0:04:18.860,0:04:23.420
The evil spirit would tell me where the money was and I would steal it.

0:04:23.420,0:04:32.480
The lack of knowledge: before exams, I would read but during the exams, everything would black out.

0:04:32.480,0:04:35.680
Tell me, what other evil things remain?

0:04:35.680,0:04:38.180
Look - what a beautiful girl.

0:04:38.180,0:04:44.300
She is bedwetting all the time, she steals...

0:04:44.300,0:04:47.880
She can enter the supermarket and steal something.

0:04:47.880,0:04:52.540
When she sleeps she bedwetts everywhere, all the time!

0:04:52.540,0:04:57.700
She can't travel, she can't go anywhere, she steals...

0:04:57.700,0:05:00.140
The bedwetting had affected me in many ways.

0:05:00.140,0:05:05.560
I could not go to my sister's house and ask to stay or go to my cousin's house.

0:05:05.560,0:05:09.760
I could not go anywhere because of the bedwetting.

0:05:09.760,0:05:15.240
I was always not happy, which was not a good thing at all.

0:05:15.240,0:05:21.560
This stealing - does it mean that your parents are poor and that is why you steal,

0:05:21.560,0:05:24.900
or it was something you could not resist?

0:05:24.900,0:05:26.700
Tell us.

0:05:26.700,0:05:30.320
My mum and dad gave me whatever I wanted.

0:05:30.320,0:05:37.460
I would go to the supermarket with a huge sum of money but pick something worth 10 or 20 naira.

0:05:37.460,0:05:39.860
How this thing comes to you?

0:05:39.860,0:05:46.140
The voice would direct me to go, that I would not be caught stealing.

0:05:46.140,0:05:47.560
There is a voice?

0:05:47.560,0:05:48.680
Yes, Sir.

0:05:48.680,0:05:49.600
You listen to that.

0:05:49.600,0:05:55.060
She said her parents gave her everything, more than what was stolen.

0:05:55.060,0:05:58.220
They have enough.

0:05:58.220,0:06:05.020
Even if she had 10 000 naira or 5 000 dollars in the pocket

0:06:05.020,0:06:10.420
she would still enter the supermarket and steal 1 dollar.

0:06:10.420,0:06:12.840
Does it make sense?

0:06:12.840,0:06:23.100
Tell your neighbour, "if you fail to realise that there are powers that cause one

0:06:23.100,0:06:35.200
to be bowed down in bondage, you will fight the wrong battle."

0:06:35.200,0:06:46.440
Now, she has 5 000 but you will see her going to the supermarket and taking 1 dollar.

0:06:46.440,0:06:51.400
What does she want to use 1 dollar for - somebody who has 5 000 dollars in the pocket?

0:06:51.400,0:06:52.880
What does she want to use it for?

0:06:52.880,0:07:01.700
That is to tell you that this is beyond human comprehension.

0:07:01.700,0:07:07.680
Ordinarily it is beyond...

0:07:07.680,0:07:11.940
There is a force that wants her to be humiliated.

0:07:11.940,0:07:15.360
There is a force that wants her to be embarrassed.

0:07:15.360,0:07:18.240
There is a force that wants her to be killed.

0:07:18.240,0:07:21.080
There is a force that wants her to be imprisoned.

0:07:21.080,0:07:24.220
There is a force that wants her to be out of circulation.

0:07:24.220,0:07:27.020
If I am talking to you let me see your hand.

0:07:27.020,0:07:30.880
There is a force.

0:07:30.880,0:07:32.480
You have to stand against it.

0:07:32.480,0:07:33.040
Stand up!

0:07:33.040,0:07:38.360
Tell your neighbour, "There is a force that wants you to be disgraced.

0:07:38.360,0:07:43.040
There is a force that wants you to be condemned.

0:07:43.040,0:07:47.360
There is a force that wants you to be imprisoned.

0:07:47.360,0:07:52.300
You have to stand against it, in the name of Jesus!

0:07:52.300,0:08:08.680
If you fail to realise that there are powers that make people to be humiliated, to be embarrassed,

0:08:08.680,0:08:12.140
you will fight a wrong battle."

0:08:12.140,0:08:17.700
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:08:17.700,0:08:21.200
You may be seated.

0:08:21.200,0:08:23.160
There are two ways;

0:08:23.160,0:08:33.020
bedwetting to embarrass her among her colleagues, to humiliate her, to make her feel inferior.

0:08:33.020,0:08:37.420
She would not be able to talk to colleagues that know she was bedwetting.

0:08:37.420,0:08:45.320
I was in a boarding school and I would wet the bed but my classmates would cover up for me.

0:08:45.320,0:08:47.940
Every time I urinated, something would wake me that I should stand up.

0:08:47.940,0:08:52.100
Then, I would turn over that mattress and leave the room.

0:08:52.100,0:08:55.040
I didn’t like watching Emmanuel TV at all.

0:08:55.040,0:08:57.080
Whenever Emmanuel TV was on, I was not happy.

0:08:57.080,0:09:00.520
I would leave the room.

0:09:00.520,0:09:03.800
My mum had to force me to come here today.

0:09:03.800,0:09:09.380
You said you bedwetted in the boarding school and your classmates knew about this, didn't you?

0:09:09.380,0:09:10.180
Yes, Sir.

0:09:10.180,0:09:11.600
What were they saying?

0:09:11.600,0:09:18.520
Most of them would say different things; like, in the hostel, I was not able to go to their rooms.

0:09:18.520,0:09:22.040
If we were doing something in any of their rooms, I could not sleep over;

0:09:22.040,0:09:23.540
I would have to come back to my room.

0:09:23.540,0:09:27.740
Most of them would insult me; it was very embarrassing.

0:09:27.740,0:09:31.080
Now you say that you did not want to watch Emmanuel TV. Why?

0:09:31.080,0:09:38.020
Each time they put Emmanuel TV on, I would leave the room and go and listen to music or watch a movie.

0:09:38.020,0:09:45.140
Those who refuse to watch Emmanuel TV in your houses - you should know the reason why.

0:09:45.140,0:09:47.920
The sister has revealed - this is a revelation.

0:09:47.920,0:09:52.960
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:09:52.960,0:09:58.740
Listen, those who don't want to see people healed...

0:09:58.740,0:10:03.860
"In the name of Jesus, rise up and walk!" - there are people that do not want to see that kind of things.

0:10:03.860,0:10:11.800
Those who do not want to see people being helped, by giving food, charity, assistance, scholarships -

0:10:11.800,0:10:12.800
