I'm talking to you - by what authority are you healing people?

0:10:30.740,0:10:32.020
I doubt that power.

0:10:32.020,0:10:37.360
Me that is talking - what am I using this authority to do?

0:10:37.360,0:10:44.220
The SCOAN Sunday Service

