She is telling you that she hated watching Emmanuel TV.

0:10:49.260,0:10:59.380
This is someone who in the past was bedwetting, stealing, because she didn't want to see

0:10:59.380,0:11:03.140
someone being delivered from stealing.

0:11:03.140,0:11:05.740
It made her feel irritated.

0:11:05.740,0:11:09.540
This is what I am doing - I steal.

0:11:09.540,0:11:16.240
