0:11:18.720,0:11:23.900
Being a thief, I would feel very condemned and worried.

0:11:23.900,0:11:27.260
I wouldn't want to watch more, if I am not ready to stop stealing.

0:11:27.260,0:11:31.260
If I am talking to you...

0:11:31.260,0:11:33.900
I would not be able to sleep that night.

0:11:33.900,0:11:35.540
I would continue to think about it.

0:11:35.540,0:11:39.640
It is better that I do not hear people talking about stealing, being delivered from stealing,

0:11:39.640,0:11:41.680
because I'm there.

0:11:41.680,0:11:43.660
Can you see?

0:11:43.660,0:11:49.800
