0:12:02.500,0:12:05.220
It would become a burden to my spirit.

0:12:05.220,0:12:07.780
It is better for me not to watch such a program.

0:12:07.780,0:12:16.780
It is better for me to watch a movie or a program where I would see people proud to be thief, to be this or that.

0:12:16.780,0:12:18.740
That would encourage my spirit.

0:12:18.740,0:12:24.540
It is better not to watch anything that would not encourage my spirit.

0:12:24.540,0:12:28.580
My mum forced me to come to SCOAN.

0:12:28.580,0:12:30.160
They forced you to come here?

0:12:30.160,0:12:31.300
Yes, sir.

0:12:31.300,0:12:33.480
How?

0:12:33.480,0:12:38.760
Before she booked the flight, I told my mum that I didn’t want to come.

0:12:38.760,0:12:40.860
She told me that I must come.

0:12:40.860,0:12:42.040
I said, "Mummy, I don’t want to come".

0:12:42.040,0:12:44.080
She said, "You must come".
She forced me.

0:12:44.080,0:12:47.520
When we got to the airport, they told us that we had missed the flight

0:12:47.520,0:12:52.600
but my mum begged them, that we couldn't miss the flight.

0:12:52.600,0:12:55.320
She then paid extra money and we came here.

0:12:55.320,0:13:04.520
When we got here for the Saturday service, under the canopy is where my mum was sat.

0:13:04.520,0:13:09.860
I left her there and walked around but didn't want to enter the church.

0:13:09.860,0:13:15.020
Then, she came inside the main auditorium and I followed her inside.

0:13:15.020,0:13:20.420
Prophet T.B. Joshua located me where I had sat down and told me to stand up.

0:13:20.420,0:13:23.480
Then, the evil spirit in me started manifesting.

0:13:23.480,0:13:29.580
Since my deliverance, I have been free – no spirit telling me to steal, I have not bedwet – nothing.

0:13:29.580,0:13:33.220
I sleep and wake up peacefully.

0:13:33.220,0:13:38.460
Now, remember that she was not the one I was talking to.

0:13:38.460,0:13:44.920
I was talking to the forth person next to her.

0:13:44.920,0:13:46.220
Come on, brother.

0:13:46.220,0:13:51.760
When I'm talking to this brother, everyone around is being observed.

0:13:51.760,0:14:11.440
Everybody around, because Jesus has eyes at the back as good as those in the front.

0:14:11.440,0:14:13.460
So, where can you go from His presence?

0:14:13.460,0:14:14.960
[Nowhere.]

