So, when I located this sister, I was in hurry to leave this brother and go to her.

0:14:23.760,0:14:25.180
OK, sit down.

0:14:25.180,0:14:30.520
Christianity and religion -

0:14:30.520,0:14:34.740
some people don't know the difference between Christianity and religion.

0:14:34.740,0:14:36.120
There is a difference.

0:14:36.120,0:14:43.560
Religious people are without spirituality

0:14:43.560,0:14:52.900
while Christians are born of the Spirit of God.

0:14:52.900,0:14:59.280
We are made in our heart to be Christians.

0:14:59.280,0:15:12.920
We are only made Christians by living in the Word and by the Word living in us.

0:15:12.920,0:15:22.020
Tell your neighbour, “We are made in our heart to be Christians”.

0:15:22.020,0:15:24.040
In other words, I mean:

0:15:24.040,0:15:35.820
we are only made Christians by living in the Word and by the Word living in us.

0:15:35.820,0:15:42.500
Ever since the man of God delivered me, I have been free; I have not bedwetted.

0:15:42.500,0:15:45.620
I have not done anything, no evil spirit has told me anything.

0:15:45.620,0:15:48.700
I just sleep and wake up peacefully.

0:15:48.700,0:15:51.800
I no longer steal or bedwet.

0:15:51.800,0:15:55.000
Man of God, I thank you so much for what you have done in my life.

0:15:55.000,0:15:57.940
Emmanuel!
(God With Us – Matthew 1:23)

0:15:57.940,0:16:01.980
I am so happy to be here, in your midst today.

0:16:01.980,0:16:10.700
My name is Mrs. Elizabeth Agboga, I am from Edo State, I reside in Abuja.

0:16:10.700,0:16:14.720
This girl beside me is my daughter.

0:16:14.720,0:16:20.800
She had been bedwetting since she was five years old.

0:16:20.800,0:16:30.760
When we came from Abuja to The SCOAN, she bedwet in the hotel that we lodged in.

0:16:30.760,0:16:32.680
Are you listening to that?

0:16:32.680,0:16:34.880
Can you see what a foolish thing?

0:16:34.880,0:16:39.500
God has taken it just like that - by His stripes.

0:16:39.500,0:16:44.600
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:16:44.600,0:16:51.120
Why there would be anyone not recognizing His death on the Calvary?

0:16:51.120,0:16:53.100
Just like that.

0:16:53.100,0:16:55.900
Tell your neighbour, "You need to be delivered."

0:16:55.900,0:17:01.020
Because it is the Spirit of prophet that recognises a prophet.

0:17:01.020,0:17:04.220
