0:17:04.220,0:17:13.620
The greatest miracle that can happen to anyone is when you begin to see what Jesus is looking at,

0:17:13.620,0:17:17.600
to go where Jesus wants you to go

0:17:17.600,0:17:24.680
and begin to look at yourself... seeing yourself having what Jesus says you have, being able to do things

0:17:24.680,0:17:27.140
Jesus says you can do.

0:17:27.140,0:17:29.040
That is the greatest miracle.

