0:18:49.540,0:18:55.120
Don't wait until you see the light at the end of the tunnel.

0:18:55.120,0:19:04.640
Tell your neighbour, “Don't wait to say, 'Thank You' until you see light at the end of the tunnel".

0:19:04.640,0:19:12.400
You are inside a tunnel and it is dark - "I will not say 'thank You' unless I get to the end".

0:19:12.400,0:19:15.780
Definitely - you will die inside the tunnel.

0:19:15.780,0:19:21.880
Those who get to the end of the tunnel are those who say "Thank You, Jesus" right inside the tunnel.

0:19:21.880,0:19:25.460
"No matter what I'm going through - thank You, Jesus. No matter what happened - thank You, Jesus.

0:19:25.460,0:19:29.620
No matter what is happening to me - thank You, Jesus. I thank You."

0:19:29.620,0:19:32.060
They thank before they get to the end of the tunnel.

0:19:32.060,0:19:38.400
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:19:38.400,0:19:42.820
If I'm talking to you...

0:19:42.820,0:19:49.520
While you are inside the tunnel, moving, trying to crawl your body in the dark, you cannot see anything,

0:19:49.520,0:19:50.820
say, "Thank You, Jesus".

